div.div: This use case diagram allows us to see the general behavior of the program. We can see that the user, after launching the application, will have to make a choice. He will be able to choose between 7 different options, the majority of which concern backup jobs. For some selected options, various information must be entered to carry out the option. The software will interact with the source and destination disks and thus move through the files, to copy the corresponding files. A log management is also provided.

div.style: text-align: justify;
div.b: "Load backup" is an optional option that we propose to implement in the future.
